Ayala Buys 50% Stake in Northwind Power, to Build Wind Power Portfolio

-- B y   C e c i l i a   Y a p
-- 
2011-03-17T00:28:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-17/ayala-buys-50-stake-in-northwind-power-to-build-wind-power-portfolio.html
  Ayala Corp. (AC)  said it bought a 50
percent stake in wind farm operator NorthWind Power Development
Corp. as part of the conglomerate’s initiative to invest in the
power sector.  “Our goal over the next five years is to build a portfolio
of power generation assets of over 1,000 megawatts,” Ayala
Corp. President Fernando Zobel de Ayala said in a disclosure to
the stock exchange today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Cecilia Yap at 
 cyap19@bloomberg.net  